## 🔍 Overview

This project implements a complete offline optimization pipeline for a Shell Eco-marathon urban concept vehicle. The goal is to minimize **Wh/km** energy consumption by computing the optimal throttle profile for a known track, using real VESC telemetry data as both the training input and validation source.

The pipeline has four stages that feed into each other:

```
Raw VESC Telemetry (.csv)
        │
        ▼
  ┌─────────────┐
  │  EDA Module │  ── extract driving modes, KPIs, anomaly detection
  └──────┬──────┘
         │
         ▼
  ┌──────────────────────────┐
  │  System Identification   │  ── step response → FOPDT transfer function
  │  G(s) = K·e^(-Ls) /     │
  │         (τ_e·s+1)(τ_m·s+1) │
  └──────┬───────────────────┘
         │  K, τ_e, τ_m, L
         ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────┐
  │  Genetic Algorithm          │  ── TF-constrained throttle profile
  │  minimize: Wh/km            │     optimization over N gene segments
  │  s.t. v_avg ≥ 10 km/h      │
  │       v_max ≤ 45 km/h      │
  └──────┬──────────────────────┘
         │  optimal_profile[N]
         ▼
  ┌─────────────────────────────┐
  │  Dijkstra / A* Path Planner │  ── per-segment speed limits from
  │  min energy path on graph   │     GPS track geometry
  └──────┬──────────────────────┘
         │
         ▼
  VESC duty_cycle lookup table
  + PID correction (Kp=0.025, Ti=2.64s)
```

---

## 🏗 System Architecture

```
sem-driveline-optimizer/
│
├── data/
│   ├── raw/                    # Raw VESC .csv exports
│   │   ├── 351_GBT_MC75.csv    # Session 1 (no GPS)
│   │   └── 2026-02-22_*.csv    # Session 2 (GPS active, 6 laps)
│   └── processed/
│       ├── timeseries.json     # Downsampled telemetry
│       ├── gps_track.json      # Cleaned GPS waypoints
│       ├── track_graph.json    # Graph nodes + edges
│       ├── tf_results.json     # Transfer function parameters
│       └── ga_results.json     # GA optimization output
│
├── modules/
│   ├── eda/
│   │   └── telemetry_eda.py    # Exploratory data analysis
│   ├── sysid/
│   │   └── transfer_function.py # Step response + TF identification
│   ├── optimizer/
│   │   └── genetic_algorithm.py # GA with TF-based vehicle simulator
│   └── pathplanner/
│       ├── graph_builder.py    # GPS → graph construction
│       └── dijkstra_astar.py   # Pathfinding algorithms
│
├── dashboards/                 # Interactive HTML outputs
│   ├── telemetry_eda.html
│   ├── transfer_function.html
│   ├── ga_optimizer.html
│   └── track_pathfinder.html
│
├── tests/
│   └── test_simulator.py
│
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

