## 🚀 Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/sem-driveline-optimizer.git
cd sem-driveline-optimizer

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

**`requirements.txt`**
```
numpy>=1.24
pandas>=2.0
matplotlib>=3.7
scipy>=1.10
```

