## 💻 Usage

### Run full pipeline

```bash
# Step 1 — EDA
python modules/eda/telemetry_eda.py --input data/raw/2026-02-22_01-25-41.csv

# Step 2 — Transfer function identification
python modules/sysid/transfer_function.py --input data/raw/351_GBT_MC75.csv

# Step 3 — GA optimization
python modules/optimizer/genetic_algorithm.py \
    --tf-params data/processed/tf_results.json \
    --v-min 10 --v-max 45 \
    --generations 100 --pop 60

# Step 4 — Path planning
python modules/pathplanner/dijkstra_astar.py \
    --input data/raw/2026-02-22_01-25-41.csv \
    --node-spacing 10 \
    --algorithm astar
```

### Open dashboards

All dashboards are standalone `.html` files — open in any browser:

```
dashboards/
├── telemetry_eda.html       ← EDA: speed, power, thermal, energy KPIs
├── transfer_function.html   ← Bode plot, step response, PID tuning
├── ga_optimizer.html        ← Convergence, chromosome, strategy comparison
└── track_pathfinder.html    ← GPS map (Canvas), speed profile, segment analysis
```

